cheatCategoryDescription: Used to describe cheats that fit in no other category.
Used to describe cheats that force a certain wild pokemon encounter.
Used to describe cheats that alter the physical apsects of gameplay.
Used to describe cheats that teleport players across the game's physical map.
Used to describe cheats that give players an infinte quantity of something.
Used to describe cheats that modify the weapon in their left hand.
Used to describe cheats that modify the weapon in their right hand.
Used to describe cheats that allow the player to start with an item.
Used to describe cheats that modify the level of in-game creatures/items.
Used to describe cheats that change the relative speed of the game.
Used to describe cheats that stack a multiplier onto values.
Used to describe cheats that give players the max quantity of something.
Used to describe cheats that modify the shooting style.
Used to describe cheats that modify items.
Used to describe cheats that unlock previously unaccessible parts of the game.
Used to describe cheats that modify the weather or game environment.
Used to describe cheats that automatically complete a part of the game.
Used to describe cheats that instantly master a skill.
Used to describe cheats that increase the game's difficulty.
Used to describe cheats that make certain enemies easier to kill.
Used to describe cheats that allow the player to choose a certain character.
Used to describe cheats that make direct alterations to the game's save file.
Used to describe cheats that modifies the weapon.
Used to describe cheats that change the starting stage of the game.
Used to describe cheats that modify the code slot.
Used to describe cheats that allow the player to access unused levels.
Used to describe cheats that modify the rank of a player, item, or level.
